HEADWORD: Offscouring
<hw>Off"scour`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Off</ets>
+ <ets>scour</ets>.]</ety> <def>That which is scoured off; hence,
